stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Pending: preview created
  Pending --> Pending: first distinct approval
  Pending --> Approved: second distinct approval and policy recheck
  Pending --> Denied: any deny decision
  Pending --> Expired: 15 minutes elapsed
  Pending --> Cancelled: requester cancels
  Pending --> Pending: identical idempotent replay
  Pending --> Invalidated: payload policy credential or target changes
  Approved --> Executing: durable workflow starts
  Executing --> Executed: Jira receipt stored
  Executing --> Failed: classified terminal failure
  Executed --> Compensating: authorized rollback
  Compensating --> Compensated: prior state restored
  Compensating --> ManualIntervention: compensation cannot safely complete
  Denied --> [*]
  Expired --> [*]
  Cancelled --> [*]
  Invalidated --> [*]
  Compensated --> [*]

